{"title":"「SDOI2016」排列计数","time_limit":3000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["SDOI","2016","组合计数","数学"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/2034#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=2034","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/2034/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/2034/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/2034"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"求有多少种长度为 $ n $ 的序列 $ A $，满足以下条件：\r\n\r\n* $ 1 \\sim n $ 这 $ n $ 个数在序列中各出现了一次；\r\n* 若第 $ i $ 个数 $ A_i $ 的值为 $ i $，则称 $ i $ 是稳定的。序列恰好有 $ m $ 个数是稳定的。\r\n\r\n满足条件的序列可能很多，序列数对 $ 10 ^ 9 + 7 $ 取模。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个数 $ T $，表示有 $ T $ 组数据。  \r\n接下来 $ T $ 行，每行两个整数 $ n $、$ m $。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出 $ T $ 行，每行一个数，表示求出的序列数。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n5\r\n1 0\r\n1 1\r\n5 2\r\n100 50\r\n10000 5000\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n0\r\n1\r\n20\r\n578028887\r\n60695423\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"测试点 1 ~ 3：$ T = 1000 $，$ n \\leq 8 $，$ m \\leq 8 $；  \r\n测试点 4 ~ 6：$ T = 1000 $，$ n \\leq 12 $，$ m \\leq 12 $；  \r\n测试点 7 ~ 9：$ T = 1000 $，$ n \\leq 100 $，$ m \\leq 100 $；  \r\n测试点 10 ~ 12：$ T = 1000 $，$ n \\leq 1000 $，$ m \\leq 1000 $；  \r\n测试点 13 ~ 14：$ T = 500000 $，$ n \\leq 1000 $，$ m \\leq 1000 $；  \r\n测试点 15 ~ 20：$ T = 500000 $，$ n \\leq 1000000 $，$ m \\leq 1000000 $。"}]}